The [[Occupy movement]] began in the [[United States]] initially with the [[Occupy Wall Street]] protests but spread to many other cities, both in the United States and worldwide.
==Locations== [[File:Occupy_SF_October_13_2011-6.jpg|thumb|right|A Protester with a sign at Occupy San Francisco]] {{see also|List of Occupy movement protest locations in the United States}}
